<h2><span id="Helpful_Instagram_video_apps"><strong>Helpful Instagram video apps</strong></span></h2>
<p>Got your tripod and your ring light ready to go? Try these Instagram video editor apps to perfect your content.</p>
<h3><a href="https://www.adobe.com/express/"><strong>Adobe Creative Cloud Express</strong></a></h3>
<p>Use Adobe Spark to <strong>automatically size Instagram videos</strong> for you, add interactive elements, and take advantage of the app’s photo and audio library.</p>
<p><a href="https://blog.hootsuite.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/instagram-video-6.png"><picture decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-large wp-image-322280">
<source type="image/webp" srcset="https://blog.hootsuite.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/instagram-video-6-620x315.png.webp 620w, https://blog.hootsuite.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/instagram-video-6-310x158.png.webp 310w, https://blog.hootsuite.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/instagram-video-6-768x390.png.webp 768w, https://blog.hootsuite.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/instagram-video-6.png.webp 1505w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px"/>
<img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://blog.hootsuite.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/instagram-video-6-620x315.png" alt="resizing instagram video dashboard in adobe creative cloud express" width="620" height="315" srcset="https://blog.hootsuite.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/instagram-video-6-620x315.png 620w, https://blog.hootsuite.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/instagram-video-6-310x158.png 310w, https://blog.hootsuite.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/instagram-video-6-768x390.png 768w, https://blog.hootsuite.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/instagram-video-6.png 1505w" sizes="(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px"/>
</picture>
</a></p>
<h3><a href="https://hootsuite.com/instagram"><strong>Hootsuite</strong></a></h3>
<p>Hootsuite’s collaborative platform is ideal for content that requires <strong>teamwork and approvals</strong>. You can also manage all your video material with Hootsuite’s content library.</p>
<p>Use the <strong>Hootsuite Planne</strong>r to pinpoint publication, plan production, and spot holes in your content calendar. And avoid lags while posting a story with multiple parts with the <strong>scheduling tools</strong>.</p>
<p><iframe title="How to make and edit Instagram Reels in 2022 | TUTORIAL with updated interface!" width="640" height="360" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/pEMg5jKpodE?enablejsapi=1&amp;038;origin=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.hootsuite.com" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>
<h3><a href="https://pictory.ai/"><strong>Pictory</strong></a></h3>
<p>Pictory is an AI tool that will help you <strong>turn text into professional-quality videos</strong> with just a few clicks.</p>
<p>How does it work? You copy and paste text into Pictory, and AI automatically creates custom video based on your input. The program pulls from a vast library of over <strong>3 million royalty-free video and music clips</strong>.</p>
<p>Pictory integrates with Hootsuite, so you can easily schedule your videos for publication without ever leaving their dashboard.</p>
<h3><a href="https://www.apalon.com/"><strong>Clipomatic</strong></a></h3>
<p>Clipomatic is an Instagram video app that lets you <strong>add live captions to social video. </strong>It’s been used by a number of high profile users, including U.S. Representative Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez and Queer Eye’s Karamo Brown.</p>
<p>Caption as you speak, or <strong>add captions to pre-recorded video</strong>. The captioning tool is available in more than 30 languages, and text can be edited and customized before posting.</p>
