<h3><a href="https://www.headliner.app/"><strong>Headliner</strong></a></h3>
<p>If you want in on the Instagram video action, but only have audio and text to work with, Headliner is for you.</p>
<p>Originally made to help promote podcasts, the app is used by Wondery, BBC, CNN and other platforms use Headliner to <strong>transcribe audio clips into shareable, animated videos</strong>.</p>
